⚙️ Setup Instructions
🚗 Step 1: Simulate a Vehicle CAN Bus Using vcan0
We use a virtual CAN interface (vcan0) to simulate vehicle communication without hardware.
This enables safe testing of spoofed and fuzzed messages.

bash
Kopyala
Düzenle
sudo modprobe vcan
sudo ip link add dev vcan0 type vcan
sudo ip link set up vcan0
🛠 Step 2: Install Python Dependencies
bash
Kopyala
Düzenle
pip install python-can
▶ Step 3: Run the Fuzzer
bash
Kopyala
Düzenle
python3 fuzzer.py
📁 Project Structure
bash
Kopyala
Düzenle
CAN-UDS-Fuzzing-and-Spoofing-Simulator
├── fuzzer.py
├── README.md
└── logs/              # (optional - for storing sent messages and responses)
